多惠","body":"啊，麻里奈小姐，{{userName}}，你們好！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"你看起來心情好好喔，你來逛街買東西嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"我買了新的音箱，所以就想說\n也順便換個新的導線好了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"這樣啊，新的音箱長怎樣呢？　我還蠻有興趣的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"是兔兔音箱","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"兔兔音箱？\n是上面有兔子插畫的音箱嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"不是，是兔兔臉的形狀的音箱。\n我去大學校慶玩的時候，在音響研究會的攤位買的！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"原來～，應該是自己做的音箱吧？\n你方便的話，希望下次能拍個照片給我看","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"當然可以！　我下次就把他帶去CiRCLE。\n他真的超級可愛的，麻里奈小姐看到一定會嚇一跳","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"呵呵，我很期待喔。\n話說回來，你去了大學校慶啊。\n和高中的文化祭是不是不太一樣？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"對啊，有賣豬肋排麵，還有很多賣平時\n吃不到的料理的攤位……\n那碗麵，加了超多肉，真的超好吃的說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"還有可以完整重現摩汀吉他獨奏的輕音社員……\n而且連髮型都一模一樣，真的有嚇到我","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"這樣啊。大學裡的人\n來自日本全國各處，\n所以一定會有很多有趣的人吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"然後，我們也有進去教學大樓裡面，\n教室非常大間，還有電梯，\n有很多花女看不見的景色……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"我總算知道大學原來是個\n比我想像中還要更有趣的地方，\n真的非常好玩！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"嗯嗯。這個世界上也有一些東西得要\n實際用眼睛去看，親自去接觸才會明白","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"對啊，我也真心這麼覺得。\n真的給了我一種「和音樂一樣」的感覺","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"和音樂一樣？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"去聽沒有聽過的聲音，\n去看沒有看過的演奏，\n就會覺得自己的心漸漸地變得更加寬闊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"這就和音樂一樣","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"確實，親自去體驗真的也很重要。\n常常也會伴隨著成長","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev201-me2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectRe